	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Dr. Floppy wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">...with 4-screen mirroring, allowing for artifact-free diagonal scrolling...</div>
<br />Actually, there are a number of ways to achieve artifact-free 8-way scrolling without 4-screen mirroring, even without the aid of mappers. All you have to do is mask out the artifacts, either with timed code (vertical mirroring) or at the expense of a few sprites (horizontal mirroring).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


