<br />
<br />True, true. I've also heard rumors that <em>diagonal</em> mirroring would allow for artifact-free eight-way scrolling (although definitive proof remains elusive).
<br />
<br />Still, I can't be the only one who yearns for a day when we don't have to perform such logistical gymnastics / sprite trade-offs?

		

